      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Earlville%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "East and West Main Street run along the Madison–Chenango county line, literally splitting the village in two.",
